query:
SELECT
                    e.id AS embed_id,
                    e.embed_type AS "embed_type:EmbedType",
                    e.name,
                    eo.url,
                    eo.last_ping_at
                FROM
                    embed_origin eo
                JOIN
                    embed e ON eo.embed_id = e.id
                WHERE
                    e.organization_id = $1
                ORDER BY
                    eo.last_ping_at DESC
                LIMIT $2;
